{"tid":2382182,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Rain 公開請粉絲推薦合作對象，網友瘋狂留言：Twice Momo & Blackpink Lisa","createTime":"2021-01-27T06:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T10:03:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"61d4385bebd90bf44aa04b3b6863344934bf51c6","tid":2382182,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_630dee5af1b04a5d2388d00ff6b2f4b9/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133298-894942.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_630dee5af1b04a5d2388d00ff6b2f4b9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133298-894942.jpg&h=55ee44e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其二選一，不如直接三人合作吧！簡直會成為歷代級畫面～。<br />\n<br />\n昨天，歌手 Rain 透通過自己的 IG 分享了獲得音樂節目1位，以及 youtube 訂閱數破百萬的感謝文。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為粉絲們的建議，收到了歌曲還和朴軫永一起上舞台表演了合作歌曲，多虧了大家《換成我吧》才獲得了1位，特別發文感謝大家。<br />\n<br />\n而為了紀念拿到1位，以及 youtube 頻道「Season B Season」突破100萬：「大家也總是希望我和女唱跳歌手合作，各位希望看到的人選會是誰呢？請推薦一下吧！我會努力促成這個合作，並在頻道上公開的。」結果湧入了大量的網友留言。<br />\n<br />\n其中，呼聲最高的兩位女歌手，分別是女團 Twice 的 Momo 和 Blackpink 的 Lisa，兩人各自在隊內都是舞蹈擔當，對此，大家都十分期待啊～！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f5195b7b066d822cc7ac49f403c21abb/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133298-894945.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f5195b7b066d822cc7ac49f403c21abb%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133298-894945.jpg&h=4506a24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖：Twice．FB／lalalalisa_m．IG）<br />\n<br />\n想必 Rain 已經看到大家的願望了，究竟他會和誰合作，呈現什麼樣的舞蹈影片呢？另外，大家最想看到 Rain 跟誰的合作呢？<br />\n<br />\n（封面圖：rain_oppa．IG／Twice．FB／lalalalisa_m．IG）"},{"pid":"43e7a67833b4f690769fbfb4d585b5fda9caa912","tid":2382182,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:15:04.000Z","msg":"支持...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213d54b90579dec8879f8a15f9299f2991127